name: os-analytics
description: OS analytics is a free, open source product designed to give developers the ability to collect and analyze user click data on their website(s). Please create a free account at https://os-analytics.com in order to receive an api key. Then, use our npm package with this api key. See our GitHub Repo for detailed instructions. Have fun collecting data!
author: Peter Larcheveque, Eric DiMarzio, David Naymon, Saw Naing
